 & = & \mathrm{P}\left(\left|\hat{\Theta}-\mathrm{E}\left(\hat{\Theta}\right)\right|>\frac{\epsilon}{\sqrt{\mathrm{V}\left(\hat{\Theta}\right)}}\sqrt{\mathrm{V}\left(\hat{\Theta}\right)}\right)\\
